SectionDefinitions.Description: PW1A: Welds on Carbon Steel / Low Temp Carbon Steel / Killed Carbon Steel piping.

Expressions.Description: Modifier != D, Size < 2, WeldingGroup = PW1A, InstallationCategory != P2
Expressions.Aggregation: Sum(x => x.NumberOfWelds * x.Size * (100 + overages.SingleOrDefault(y => y.Unit == "DiaInch" & y.MaterialGroupCode == x.MaterialGroupCode).Overage) / 100)
Expressions.Criteria: Where(x => !x.Modifier.Equals("D") && x.Size < 2 && x.WeldingGroupCode.Equals("PW1A") && !x.InstallationCategory.Name.Equals("P2"))
